 NRs at the PG boundary one can\nconclude that along this boundary, as well as in x_{c2}, all bosons disappear.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Wed, 12 May 2010 16:24:23 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Mon, 31 May 2010 09:19:32 GMT"},{"version":"v3","created":"Tue, 10 Jan 2012 17:53:35 GMT"}],"update_date":"2015-03-17"}
